thread.title: Brett Small

author: Brett Small
title: Brett Small
text: After leaving a competitor serviced office, we have been very pleasantly surprised with the quality of the 710 Collins st office and the team who go above and beyond to look after us. The office isn't too big, is very quiet and has excellent facilities. It's proximity to public transport and CBD/Docklands makes it the perfect location for our business. I would highly recommend this office to others looking for a new home for their business.
